'''Badara''' (also Bodara and Ptretsik) is a village in the [[Khojali Rayon]] of [[Azerbaijan]]. Since the [[Nagorno-Karabakh war]] the town has been administered by the ''de facto'' [[Republic of Artsakh]] as part of [[Askeran Region|Askeran Province]].<ref>http://census.stat-nkr.am/nkr/1-1.pdf</ref>

