[[File:Cape_Charles,_Labrador,_NL,_1908.jpg|thumb|right| Cape St.Charles, 1908]]
'''Cape St. Charles''' is a headland on the coast of [[Labrador]] in the [[Canada|Canadian]] province of Newfoundland and Labrador. At [[longitude]] 55°37'15"W it is the easternmost point of continental [[North America]].

