{{orphan|date=January 2018}}
'''Old Airport''' ({{Lang-ms|Lapangan Terbang Lama}}) is an area in [[Bandar Seri Begawan]], [[Brunei]]. It is the common name given to the former site of the [[Brunei Airport]] (hence the name) and is now the location of several government offices.
== Government offices == The former terminal building of the Brunei Airport has become the office of the Government Printing Department.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.printing.gov.bn/Theme/Home.aspx|title=Home - Jabatan Percetakan|last=|first=|date=|website=www.printing.gov.bn|language=ms|archive-url=|archive-date=|dead-url=|access-date=2018-01-10}}</ref> Its vicinity is also the location of various government buildings which belong to two ministries and several government departments. These include: * [[Ministry of Education (Brunei)|Ministry of Education]] * Ministry of Development<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.mod.gov.bn/SitePages/Hubungi%20Kami.aspx|title=Kementerian Pembangunan - Hubungi Kami|last=|first=|date=|website=www.mod.gov.bn|language=ms|archive-url=|archive-date=|dead-url=|access-date=2018-01-10}}</ref> * Mail Processing Centre * Public Works Department * Brunei-Muara District Office * Public Service Commission<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.spa.gov.bn/SitePages/Hubungi%20Kami.aspx|title=Pejabat Suruhanjaya Perkhidmatan Awam - Hubungi Kami|last=|first=|date=|website=www.spa.gov.bn|language=ms|archive-url=|archive-date=|dead-url=|access-date=2018-01-10}}</ref> * Department of Electrical Services<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.des.gov.bn/SitePages/Contact%20Us.aspx|title=Department of Electrical Services - Contact Us|website=www.des.gov.bn|language=en-GB|access-date=2018-01-10}}</ref> * Housing Development Department<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.mod.gov.bn/housing/bm/SitePages/Hubungi%20Kami.aspx|title=Jabatan Kemajuan Perumahan - Hubungi Kami|last=|first=|date=|website=www.mod.gov.bn|language=ms|archive-url=|archive-date=|dead-url=|access-date=2018-01-10}}</ref> * {{Lang|ms|Dewan Bahasa dan Pustaka Brunei}} * Information Department<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.information.gov.bn/SitePages/Contact%20Us.aspx|title=Information Department - Contact Us|website=www.information.gov.bn|language=en-GB|access-date=2018-01-10}}</ref> * Anti-Corruption Bureau<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.bmr.gov.bn/SitePages/Contact%20Us.aspx|title=Anti-Corruption Bureau - Contact Us|website=www.bmr.gov.bn|language=en-US|access-date=2018-01-10}}</ref> * Agriculture Department * Survey Department * Land Department
